Joseph T . 
  Brennan Jr . 
  of Norwell was found with a home full of bomb-making materials  . 
  Police searched the home after an incident on Saturday night where Brennan blew up his car while smoking a cigarette near gun powder . 
  Brennan was arraigned from his hospital bed on Monday and pleaded not guilty to possession of an infernal device . 
  Police also found the home of Benjamin Young in Hingham with bomb- making materials . 
  Brennan called himself an 'idiot' after the incident and said he lit a cigarette with the gunpowder in his car . 
  He was admitted to hospital with minor injuries . 
 